<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>

import {onMounted} from "vue";

export default {
  name: "Home",
  props: ['mqttClient'],
  setup(props){
    onMounted(()=> {

      props.mqttClient
          .then((client) => {
            client.on('connect', ()=> {
              console.log("mqttClient: " + mqttClient)
              return client;
            })
          })
          .catch((err) => {
            console.log(err)
            return null;
          });
    })

    console.log(props.mqttClient)
  }
}

</script>
